@startuml

!include configuration/skinParams.puml
!include configuration/definitions.puml

actor user
view IterationView
controller AssignActivityController
model Iteration
model ActivityDao
model Activity
model Member

user -right-> IterationView
note on link
    assignActivityToMember(activityId, memberId)
end note
IterationView -down-> AssignActivityController
note on link
    assignActivityToMember(activityId, memberId)
end note
AssignActivityController --> ActivityDao
note on link
    patch(activity)
end note

IterationView --> Iteration
IterationView --> Member
IterationView --> Activity

AssignActivityController --> Activity
Activity o--> Member
@enduml
